The '''Gujarat Environment Management Institute''' (GEMI) is an Autonomous Institute under the Forests and Environment Department of [[Government of Gujarat]]. GEMI has been involved in the overall conservation, protection and management of environment since 1999 and  has taken up various studies and research projects.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/ahmedabad/Gujarat-bags-three-national-awards/articleshow/50851735.cms |title=Gujarat bags three national awards - Times of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2016-02-04 |accessdate=2016-09-30}}</ref>

